</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
   By KIERAN COOKE
</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>
   KUALA LUMPUR
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
Renong, the Malaysian conglomerate which is closely connected to the
governing United Malays National Organisation political party, has announced
pre-tax profits of MDollars 107m (USDollars 39m) for the six months months
to December 31 1993, writes Kieran Cooke in Kuala Lumpur.
